{"tid":1296081,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"最終目標只有一個：港共政權，請勿失焦","createTime":"2019-07-08T08:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T09:51:08.000Z","uid":190579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5528ff70251b25186cf31731d9cb4400554cc4c8","tid":1296081,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:54:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">繼續屌尻警犬，同時注意失焦</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n警犬係一個共同敵人，用嚟團結己方。最終目標唔係警犬同林奠，係整個港共政權！<br />\n我唔同意政府而家刻意用警犬嚟群眾鬥群眾。用警犬鬥我哋只會將民怨愈鬥愈旺，我地只會愈嚟愈團結，愈嚟愈多同路人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警犬同林奠同一條船，呢一點文宣必須強調，唔可以比港共獨善其身。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@hkjohnsonyeung/6%E6%9C%8816%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B-%E4%B8%89-%E6%95%B2%E6%8E%89%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%94%AF%E6%9F%B1-fa2441adf289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40hkjohnsonyeung%2F6%25E6%259C%258816%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E4%25B8%2589-%25E6%2595%25B2%25E6%258E%2589%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%259F%25B1-fa2441adf289&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=589f6676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@hkjohnsonyeung/6%E6%9C%8816%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B-%E4%B8%89-%E6%95%B2%E6%8E%89%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%94%AF%E6%9F%B1-fa2441adf289</a>"},{"pid":"435c0a832a2d0d08651aa2cc3cfa64c2cd230c66","tid":1296081,"uid":1400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2322d1e837fc83531945ee59243dd9ab4760fdf8","tid":1296081,"uid":191740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"